headline: AIG Appoints Scott Leney as Regional President, AIG Asia Pacific
summary: NEW YORK, December 15, 2025--American International Group, Inc. (NYSE: AIG) today announced that Scott Leney has been appointed Regional President, AIG Asia Pacific. Mr. Leney will lead AIG’s businesses in Australia, New Zealand, Singapore, Indonesia, Malaysia, Thailand, South Korea, Hong Kong, Taiwan, Vietnam, and the Philippines.
